name: sqlcl
desc: Oracle SQLcl is the modern command-line interface for the Oracle Database
caveats:
sqlcl requires Java 8+. You can install the latest version with:
  brew install --cask temurin

To use sqlcl, you may need to add the $(brew --prefix)/Caskroom/sqlcl/21.3.2.287.1503/sqlcl/bin directory
to your PATH environment variable, e.g. (for Bash shell):
  export PATH=$(brew --prefix)/Caskroom/sqlcl/21.3.2.287.1503/sqlcl/bin:"$PATH"
